<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Referat af årsmøde i Danske Kvindelige Lægers Forening</strong></p>
<p style="margin-left: 150px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri;">Tirsdag d. 24 maj 2016 kl. 17.00 </span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 90px; text-indent: 65.2pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri;">Frederiksberg Hospital, </span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 90px; text-indent: 29.2pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri;">Auditoriet, Hovedvejen, Indgang 4 </span></p>
<ol>
<li>Velkomst ved formand Sarah Carlsen</li>
<li>Uddeling af Agnethe Løvgreens Legat ved Kirsten Salado-Rasmussen samt indlæg af årets legatmodtagere</li>
</ol>
<p style="margin-left: 30px; text-indent: -18pt;">Årets legatmodtagere er:</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Læge Kirstine Nauerby Heltoft, Arbejdsmed., BBH &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;30.000 kr.</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Stud.med. Katrine Begtrup, Center for hæmofili og trombose, AUH &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;30.000 kr.</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Læge, ph.d. Katherina Farr, Med. Endokrinologisk afd., AUH &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 30.000 kr.</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Stud.med. Ebba Mannheimer, Inf.med., RH &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;30.000 kr. </span></p>
<ol>
<li><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri;">Orientering om foreningens større aktiviteter: </span></li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri;"> Myanmar Projektet v. Birte Holm Sørensen </span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri;"> Mentorordning/Cafemøder v. Johanne Bjerre Lindboe </span></li>
</ul>
